data.title: Afonso I "o Conquistador" (Afonso I "o Conquistador") "'The Conqueror' of Portugal" Henriques rei de Portugal (1110
data.meta_description: Afonso I "o Conquistador" Henriques was born on July 25, 1110 in Guimaraes, Braga, Portugal, son of Henri de Bourgogne and Teresa Alfonso. He was married about 1146 to Mafalda de Sab√≥ia, they gave birth to 1 child. He died on December  6, 1185 in Coimbra, Portugal. This information is part of Family tree Homs by George Homs on Genealogy Online.
